From d4db5de9b2078875ef814a20a9f24205cabce355 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Pooventhiran G <pooventh@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 8 Jul 2025 12:08:10 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 03/13] AP MLD: Process Link Reconfiguration Request frame for
 ML Setup links

A non-AP MLD can change the ML setup links (adding a new link or
removing an existing link) by using `Link Reconfiguration to Setup Links`
procedure, as per IEEE P802.11be/D7.0.

Add support for an AP MLD to parse the Link Reconfiguration Request
frame and setup context with necessary information.

Reviewed-by: Rohan Dutta <drohan@qti.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Pooventhiran G <pooventh@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
